    "Id": 10,
    "Content": "It will automatically prompt for password when necessary\n* This script will ask you to install firmware, bluetooth and wifi driver one by one\n* Tested on Ubuntu with linux 7.0 kernel\n\n### 🚀 Easy Automatic Fix (Recommended for Arch Based System)\nIf you want to quickly fix your WiFi and Bluetooth on any modern kernel, follow these steps:\n\nMake the script executable if not already",
    "ContentSha": "mePv+dKi33GgBsipTP7w17LuKK0uJFEcWDnOzcT3CuI=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "它会在必要时自动提示输入密码  \n* 该脚本将依次要求您安装固件、蓝牙和WiFi驱动程序  \n* 在使用Linux 7.0内核的Ubuntu上测试通过  \n\n### 🚀 简易自动修复（推荐用于基于Arch的系统）  \n如果您想在任何现代内核上快速修复WiFi和蓝牙，请按照以下步骤操作：  \n\n如果脚本尚未可执行，请赋予执行权限  ",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 11,
    "Content": "```\nchmod +x ./fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "ContentSha": "TrDah6izESr6AgEsbTRKYlkukuyBf9MPB55vEobFX/w=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```\nchmod +x ./fix_my_wifi.sh\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 12,
